{
  "stem": "27390.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were showers in the, in the block.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was used-- when the Red Cross used to send their commission, they were shown this camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were three, we were three weeks in this camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the food was not bad either.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After the three weeks, guards came and took us away from there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were taken to a place called Budy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I've never seen a Red Cross commission.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But apparently they used to come.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know how often, but this camp was used for Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were proper blocks, brick-built blocks, not like the other prefab blocks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, we were taken to a place, which was called Budy, that was a farm that supplied food to the main camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we, I was allotted with the other 26-- from the 131 boys, they divided us into three or four groups.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And 26 of us were allotted to this camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we looked after the horses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had to make sure-- we had to get up very early in the morning to feed the horses, to clean the horses, and in the evening as well, when they came back.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Some of them were riding horses for the SS.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And some of them, they were working horses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in the evening we had to feed and clean the horses again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So it was a very long day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "By the time we finished with the horses was about 9 o'clock at night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we just managed to lay down for a few hours.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And in the morning, the same thing all over again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That went on for seven days a week, because horses don't know Saturday or Sunday.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You have to work with them all the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
